Brkn,be,provides,a,Url,shortening,service,on,its,regular,web,page,This,feature,is,also,available,as,a,simple,REST,API,that,responds,to,GET,or,POST,requests,to,shorten,the,submitted,URL,The,shortened,URL,can,also,be,used,to,track,click,statistics,such,as,unique,visitors,visiting,countries,and,browsers